description:
Sell Yourself Rich was created by Coach Carl who started his 16 year coaching, seminar and speaking company from his truck with a cell phone and phone book. Sell Yourself Rich is about leading with your strengths, confidence and formulas to serve your ideal clients and customers so they crave to do business with you. While far too many entrepreneurs, business owners and professionals sell themselves poor or sell themselves short, this program shows you exact ways to set yourself up for success by utilizing a NO resistance or pushy approach. Learn to be a person that inspires, influences and deliver your ideal clients/custmers. 

You receive 40 hands on, educational and at times, entertaining videos, with complete handouts and quines to test your knowledge. You will also benefit from bonus videos and access to Coach Carl, the course instructor.
title: Sell Yourself Rich
